{"3951460": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "黑尾偵探與血月事件", "steam_appid": 3951460, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黑尾偵探與血月之謎》是一款融合黑色偵探風格的視覺小說，交織著懸疑、浪漫與露骨H場景，玩家的抉擇將深刻影響命運走向。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3951460/extras/1dc6476b525446df109cab05b3a7b104.poster.avif?t=1776180209\" width=1170 height=854 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3951460/extras/1dc6476b525446df109cab05b3a7b104.webm?t=1776180209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>故事🕵️</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >血月輝光下的費爾格雷夫正腐朽崩壞。每逢四年一度的血月之夜，男人們神秘消失，掠食者失控暴食，犯罪率直線飆升。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >曾是費爾格雷夫最銳利的偵探，黑尾如今卻成了無群之狼——遭放逐、沉溺酒癮、無人問津。當舊情復燃之際，又一名男子在血月下消失，他被迫重返這座城市的陰影深處。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >黑尾能否揭開真相，抑或被體內飢渴吞噬？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>暗影中的慾望💔</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3951460/extras/3bcc63e3f6c577240a3cbee5629f8051.avif?t=1776180209\" width=1318 height=1212 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3951460/extras/df95e6198236e121c448b85a877687f5.avif?t=1776180209\" width=1318 height=1212 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3951460/extras/83115f52e932e1c443ca152bed27ffd9.avif?t=1776180209\" width=1318 height=1212 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲特色🔥</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>豐富的黑色偵探故事—</stro